{"tid":1540613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達：林鄭落區的陷阱","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:57:24.000Z","uid":210711,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"766338b91b406f03952daaf1c2477e9dd8e15d16","tid":1540613,"uid":210711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"【林鄭落區的陷阱】<br />\n林鄭話嚟緊會同司局長一齊落區，呢個就係佢所講嘅「對話平台」。<br />\n我之前節目一早預測過佢會咁做，點解咁做？係為左阻斷「流水抗爭」。<br />\n<br />\n因為現在的示威時間與地點，完全不可測，黑警疲於奔命，突發狀況也容易將更多巿民街坊捲入其中，讓抗爭一方不斷補充新血。<br />\n<br />\n定期落區，可以將示威定時集中係落區地點，只要截停港鐵巴士等交通，隔離示威區域，就可以集中鎮壓，又可以讓其他巿民及早知悉示威爆發時地，及早避開。<br />\n<br />\n落區十幾廿次，連續進行大規模拘捕，期望可將流水變死水。<br />\n<br />\n這是林鄭落區的如意算盤。<br />\n不過，只要大家無視她的落區，這個算盤就打不響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，參與林鄭政府的對話平台，等於認同了政府正在跟進處理，除非你打算襲擊官員（我不主張），否則到場示威，也算是參與對話，等於幫政權buy time、維穩。<br />\n<br />\n在和平時勢，政黨到咨詢會場示威，表態一下爭取選票無妨。如今，黑警的鎮壓，已到達危害性命的地步，現在不應與極權建立任何對話關係。<br />\n<br />\n所以，應該完全無視林鄭落區！<br />\n趁佢落區，大家應該去其他區遊玩～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登仔自己諗下，要唔要因人廢言</span>"},{"pid":"579b6e6bcaf88014b2343fbb7aa6134eab0a717c","tid":1540613,"uid":210711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxBSR3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxBSR3q.png&h=02af6823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fbfa3d3d9e35d61090c0d64e079378b4e360df","tid":1540613,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa889SFe.jpg&h=3fb438bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"12085860087bb252983087d9afec833583af3490","tid":1540613,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"fbdab77a088aa29da9215efecaafeae29759736e","tid":1540613,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4370a1133ea2caf2b2db37918e6298ea40f2172","tid":1540613,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"計我話狗隊記者會都應該杯葛"},{"pid":"7210c37054424ccc80fc58bd7e7a434baa55d97f","tid":1540613,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re